text:
Quite a big variety of ingredients to choose from. I tried the laksa base and it’s not too thick or bland for pairing with the ingredients.

There are a few soup bases you can choose from like Mala, Tomyum and laksa. You can also choose your carbohydrate that include noodles, beehoon  and rice. A hearty and filling meal.

my favourite yong tau foo place :”) my go to! i would travel down specifically just for this yong tau foo. super good, chili is really amazing too. have to try their deep fried tau kee w fish paste and you tiao with fish paste always always my constant ingredients. mala soup is great!

the staff is really nice too especially the lady and skinny male staff :”) always feel very welcomed when i purchase from them. they’re extremely friendly, do their best in cooking their food! i love it so so so much

One of the best yongtaufoo around. Probably the best 24-hour ytf I’ve ever had. Laksa gravy is tasty and gao. Soup is also moreish and they prepare every serving properly, packing gravy/fried items separately. Ingredients are good too.

Special shout out to the service staff (especially the one on the night shift!) they have amazing memory and are always super nice and helpful.

Great place, always happy to be back.
Good selection of halal yong tau foo.. 24hrs some more… come try try
There is a worm in the soup. Private message and video was sent in IG but no one get back.
